headline: Motorola Solutions Completes Acquisition of Theatro
summary: CHICAGO, March 06, 2025--Motorola Solutions (NYSE: MSI) today announced it has completed its acquisition of Theatro Labs, Inc. ("Theatro"), maker of AI and voice-powered communication and digital workflow software for frontline workers, based in Richardson, Texas.
